data.description: Welcome to a truly impeccable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that is ready for you to move in and make it your own. This charming residence is perfectly situated in a serene community, offering the best of both worlds. You'll be just a short 5-minute drive from the vibrant heart of downtown Conway, where local culture, dining, and events await. And when the allure of the beach, shops, restaurants, and entertainment of Myrtle Beach's Grand Strand beckons, you're only 25 minutes away.  Walking into the home you'll see a spacious living area space with two bedrooms and a bathroom off to the left side. Through the living space you'll enter the kitchen and a beautiful built in desk/office space on the left. The back half of the home offers the primary bedroom to the left and the spacious one car garage to right. The main living area has LVP flooring, providing both durability and aesthetic. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, including a brand-new microwave and garbage disposal, both added in 2023. In addition, a generous pantry closet helping with all your storage needs. There is a utility sink in the laundry room.  The backyard is perfect for your morning coffee or an evening beverage with a private screened in patio. Off the front of the house is a large porch that invites you to entertain and relax, and an exterior shade system ensures you can enjoy this space at any time of day while maintaining your privacy. A spacious, clean one-car garage provides secure parking and extra storage space.  The neighborhood is surrounded by mature landscaping, and there's a park right across from the development, ideal for outdoor enjoyment and leisure. Schedule a viewing and experience the beauty, comfort, and prime location of this home for yourself.
